oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Note From Bill Denny
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Cedarwood Publishing Company; Denny, Bill (J. William); Offset printing;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: A black and white negative framed by a masking sheet announcing "Note! From Bill Denny" alongside the Cedarwood Publishing Company name and address and blank spaces for the name of the person for whom the note is for and the date. The negative would have been used to create a matching printing plate.
